      "intro_text": "This certificate is issued in compliance with the laboratory internal procedure PRO-CAL-MST-003. The results refer exclusively to the identified DIGITAL thermometer and to the declared calibration conditions. After having identified the F. taratura, the calibration function is: T = A \\u00b7 D + B. The calibration was determined over 6 calibration points (0 °C to 125 °C) using a Fluke 1502A metrology well readout and Pt100 reference thermometer.",
